yingyinNormal.en: You were once a user of Mr. Gross's networking site, Mr. Fishbein?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你曾是格罗斯先生社交网站的一名用户？

yingyinNormal.en: So you blame the NSA for losing you 20% of your user base? Yes.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你认为是国安局导致贵公司失去20％的用户? 是的。

yingyinNormal.en: Thank you. I thought we might start by talking about the user interface.
yingyinNormal.zh: 谢谢，我认为我们可以先从用户界面开始讨论。

yingyinNormal.en: Naresh, I think we should talk to someone about that user abnormality.
yingyinNormal.zh: 纳雷什，我觉得咱们应该汇报一下那个用户异常的问题。

yingyinNormal.en: And the NSA has asked us over and over to provide user information from our social networking sites.
yingyinNormal.zh: 而国安局还一遍又一遍地要求我们，让我们交出自己社交网站上的用户信息。

yingyinNormal.en: A while back, YouTube changed its user interface from a star-based rating system to a thumbs-up rating system.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不久前，YouTube把它用户界面的评分系统从打星改成了点赞。

yingyinNormal.en: Yes. And does Scabbit reward you for these efforts? Yeah. I have more Pimp Points than any other user.
yingyinNormal.zh: 是的。「瞎掰网」有无给予你回报呢？是的，我的「皮条分」比其他任何用户都多。

yingyinNormal.en: Why did you call him? Dante Pryor is a Scabbit user who goes by the online name of Chubbysocks52. It's one of the names that was released to us.
yingyinNormal.zh: 为什么你要求他出庭？但丁·普雷尔是「瞎掰网」，用户网名为「肥袜52」，是我们收到的名单中的一位。

yingyinNormal.en: The future world, business will not focus on the size, business will not focus on standardization and power, they will focus on the flexibility, nimbleness, customization and user-friendliness.
yingyinNormal.zh: 未来的世界，企业将不再会关注于规模，企业不再会关注于标准化和权力，他们会关注于灵活性、敏捷性、个性化和用户友好。

yingyinNormal.en: A single Yellowjacket offers the user unlimited influence to carry out protective actions.
yingyinNormal.zh: 一件黄蜂战衣使用者就可以拥有无限潜能以实施防御举措。

yingyinNormal.en: And based on the fact that Mr. Geller is intravenous drug user. What? Yes, heroin and crack.
yingyinNormal.zh: 而且他使用静脉注射毒品。什么？ 是的，海洛因与快克。

yingyinNormal.en: Now, GHB gives the user a feeling of euphoria, but take it in combination with alcohol and you stop breathing.
yingyinNormal.zh: G水能够让服用者极度兴奋，但与酒精混合，会让人停止呼吸。

yingyinNormal.en: Windows that don't open, multi user linens, keys shaped like credit cards as if one walks around with unassigned slots in one's wallet.
yingyinNormal.zh: 打不开的窗户，N个人用过的床单，卡式的钥匙，好像谁的钱包都有空的卡槽似的。

yingyinNormal.en: It was just role-playing. It was harmless. Until the money. She found his user name on Venmo. She sent $2,500 to cover hospital expenses. Expenses that didn't exist.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那只是角色扮演。无伤大雅。直到那笔钱。她在Venmo小额转账上找到了他的账号。给他转了2500美金的住院费。但那住院费不存在。

yingyinNormal.en: Maybe I'm not being clear. On YouCast, you've been chatting with my daughter for months. Your user name is 'fish_n_chips'. Your mother was in the hospital. Right? What's YouCast?
yingyinNormal.zh: 可能我没有表达清楚。这几个月，你一直在"换你了"直播网站上和我女儿聊天。你的网名是"fish_n_chips"。你妈妈生病住院。对吧？什么是"换你了"？
